</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="99.[189,1398,368,429]" pageId="99" pageNumber="100">
Nichuguard is now part of the growing town Chumukedima near Dimapur and the 
<typeStatus box="[1161,1212,369,395]" pageId="99" pageNumber="100">type</typeStatus>
locality is most likely lost for this species.
</paragraph>
